<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Biyomedikal Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6247</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 134</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">20th Century Political and Social History</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">20. the century political and social history course will include the leading political, social, cultural and economic developments of the last century. The subject of the course on the history of the century, which Hobsbawm describes as the &quot;age of extremism&quot;, is the holistic history of the century, in which extreme growing, producing and consuming, increasingly globalised and extreme ideological campings took place. Ideologies such as fascism-Nazism, socialism and totalitarian state systems, the two great World Wars, The establishment of the Eastern Bloc and NATO, the Cold War period and societies in this period are among the main topics of the course. In addition, important political developments such as independence movements in Asia, Africa and the Americas, the establishment of Israel and changing balances in the Middle East, the Iranian Revolution, the Cuban crisis will be examined. 20. The century is the time when science develops and becomes social. Science, technology development, industrialization, modernization and social transformation, the development of consumer culture, the &apos;68 movement, anti-apartheid movements, the Asia-Africa-South America independence movements, military coups, working-class movements, the second wave of feminism, Iranian Green Movement, the anti-globalization movement such as social-cultural movements of the main topics of the course.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412477&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Biyomedikal Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6247</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 135</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Academic Turkish I</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
