<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">LEARNING ANCIENT WORLD HISTORY, ANCIENT EGYPT, ANCIENT GREECE AND ROME, ANATOLIAN ANCIENT CIVILIZATIONS, HISTORICAL, ARCHAEOLOGICAL, ETHNOGRAPHIC, ANTHROPOLOGICAL, GEOGRAPHICAL TRANSFERS TOWARDS WORLD HERITAGE AND WONDERS</Data></Cell>
