<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Biyomedikal Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6247</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">BME 319</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Optimization</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">7</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Students will have gained the ability to create a formal optimization problem, have basic knowledge of numerical optimization algorithms, and will have sufficient understanding of the strengths and weaknesses of these approaches.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412355&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Biyomedikal Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6247</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">BME 326</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Systems Physilogy</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">7</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">This class focuses on understanding physiology –the functioning of a living organism and its component parts. This requires going beyond memorization of facts to acquire an understanding of how and why the body functions the way it does, and what happens when it does not function properly.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412357&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Biyomedikal Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6247</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">BME 409</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Clinical Engineering</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">7</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">7</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Students will understand and interpret Medical Device Regulations, Medical Device Classification, Certification, associated Risks and Adverse Events; learn to access Medical Device Standards (both European and international) and use them; will acquire expertise to iniate the Clinical Engineering Department in Healthcare Facilities and run device calibration, testing and performance measurements services; will learn physiological effects of electrical currents and be able to take necessary actions in the Hospitals to avoid electrical shock incidents and acccidents.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412502&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Biyomedikal Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6247</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">BME 410</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Healthcare Facility Guidelines and Standards</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">7</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">7</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">The students will learn about the current standards and guidelines for Electrical Safety and Grounding, Medical Gases, Clean Room, Hazardeous materials, Sterilization in Hospitals.
They acquire the knowledge,of basic Design principles for the Healthcare Facility;
electrical leakage currents/shock currents, medical gas purity, clean room particle counting and classification, medical device sterility and hazardeous materials classification</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412506&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Biyomedikal Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6247</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">BME 419</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=448513&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Biyomedikal Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6247</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">BME 506</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Medical Image Processing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">7</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">The course will introduce the basic physical principles that enable information about the tissues in the body to be received in the form of signals, taking into account the main physical principles used, under 4 main headings: transmission-based methods (for example, X-ray), reflection-based methods (for example, Ultrasound), emission-based methods (in ex. SPECT / PET) and resonance-based methods (MRI / fMRI).</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412550&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Biyomedikal Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6247</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">BME 509</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412571&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Biyomedikal Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6247</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">BME 510</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Biosensors</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">7</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Overview of biosensor applications,Desired characteristics of biosensors,Chemical reactions,Enzymes,Cells,Antibodies,Nucleic Acids (RNA and DNA),Labels,Immobilization, Seismic (mass) and thermal sensors, Electrochemical sensors, Optical sensors</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412564&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
