<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">7</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Fate of the drugs in the body and route of them from administration to excretion, conventional drugs and their drawbacks, main goals and benefits of controlled release systems, the methods to provide release of the drugs in a controlled manner, mechanisms of controlled drug release, factors affecting the release rate and fate of the drugs, the concept of drug bioavailability, design and preparation methods of controlled release systems, materials used as drug carriers, classification of controlled release systems based on their shapes and release rates, targeted and injectable controlled release systems, and examples for applications.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412579&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
