<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">In this course, health quality management, process analysis tools used to assess cause-effect analysis and statistical tools for system analysis are taught .</Data></Cell>
