</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Biyomedikal Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6247</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">MBT 521</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Principles of Biotechnology</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">8</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">9</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Why is biotechnology? What are cell typing techniques? What is cell culture and where is it used? What is the importance of enzymes in biotechnology? How is microbial culture technology and fermentation applications used? What are the principles of protein engineering, bioinformatics and molecular modeling, vaccine development, tissue engineering, diagnosis, drug development, moral issues in applications, and patent?</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412461&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Biyomedikal Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6247</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">MBT 535</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Introduction to Grafics and Molecular Modelling</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">7</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">9</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1. Useful concepts in Molecular Modelling
2. An Introduction to computational quantum mechanics
3. Advanced ab initio Methods, Density Functional Theory and Solid-State Quantum Mechanics
4. Emprical Force Field Models: Molecular Mechanics
5. Energy Minimisation and Related Methods for Exploring the energy surface
6. Computer Simulation Methods
7. Molecular Dynamics Simulation Methods
8. Monte Carlo Simulation Methods
9. Conformational Analysis
10. Protein Structure Prediction, Sequence Analysis and Protein Folding
11. Four Challenges in Molecular Modelling: Free Energies, Solvation, Reactions and Solid-state Defects
12. The Use of Molecular Modelling and Chemoinformatics to Discover and Design New Molecules
13. The Use of Graphical Softwares for the visualization</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412370&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Biyomedikal Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6247</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">MBT 549</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Fungal Biotechnology</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">7</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">9</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1 Fungal Diversity, Physiology and Architecture
2 Fungal Growth
3 Fungal Metabolism and Metabolic Engineering
4 Fungi as Model Organisms
5 Molecular Tool Kits for Fungal Biotechnology-I
6 Molecular Tool Kits for Fungal Biotechnology-II
7 Genetic Manipulation Systems for Yeast-I
8 Genetic Manipulation Systems for Yeast-II
9 Fungal Gene &amp; Genome Editing Technologies
10 Application of Genetic Engineering for Strain Improvement in Filamentous Fungi
11 Fungi as Producers of Biopharmaceuticals-I
12 Fungi as Producers of Biopharmaceuticals-II
13 Systems Biology of Fungi-I
14 Systems Biology of Fungi-II</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412371&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
