<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">8</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">to understand how the endocrine system functions as the body’s second major control system. Be able to describe the major endocrine organs, their primary functions and diseases associated with them.</Data></Cell>
