<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Biyomedikal Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6247</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">BME 321</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Electrical and Electronic Circuits</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Students are expected to learn how to develop and employ circuit models for elementary electronic components, e.g., resistors, sources, inductors, capacitors, diodes and transistors.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412513&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Biyomedikal Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6247</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">BME 321</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Electrical and Electronic Circuits</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Students are expected to become adept at using various methods of circuit analysis, including simplified methods such as series-parallel reductions, voltage and current dividers, and the node method.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412513&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Biyomedikal Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6247</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">BME 321</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Electrical and Electronic Circuits</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Students are expected to appreciate the consequences of linearity, in particular the principle of superposition and Thevenin Norton equivalent circuits; Gain an intuitive understanding of the role of power flow and energy storage in electronic circuits.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412513&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Biyomedikal Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6247</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">BME 321</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Electrical and Electronic Circuits</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Students are expected to develop the capability to analyze and design simple circuits containing non-linear elements such as transistors using the concepts of load lines, operating points and incremental analysis.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412513&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Biyomedikal Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6247</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">BME 321</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Electrical and Electronic Circuits</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Students are expected to learn how the primitives of Boolean algebra are used to describe the processing of binary signals and to use electronic components such as MOSFET&apos;s as building blocks in electronically implementing binary functions.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412513&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
