<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">By the end of the course, students will generate visionary concepts for utilizing biomaterials to construct proper scaffolds for artificial tissue generation to address global diseases.</Data></Cell>
