<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Select appropriate numerical methods (e.g., bisection, Newton, secant) for solving linear and nonlinear equations, implement their algorithms, and apply them on a computer.</Data></Cell>
