<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">11</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Designing Effective Slides: Using visuals to enhance your presentation, avoiding clutter, and choosing appropriate fonts and colors.
