<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">• Swidler, Ann (2001) selections from “Finding Culture,” chapter 1, “Repertoires,” chapter 2, “Conclusion: How Culture Matters” in Talk of Love (The University of Chicago Press,), pp. 11-23, 24-34, 160-180.</Data></Cell>
